data.description: Established over 40 years ago, The Moorings Yacht & Country Club is one of Vero Beach’s most prestigious, private, member owned clubs. Located on the shores of the Indian River Lagoon, a piece of paradise awaits you. Here you’ll find a challenging Pete Dye designed 18 hole golf course, 9 Har-Tru® tennis courts open for day and night play, a state-of-the art fitness center, pool & spa, an active yacht club and deep water dockage, a dynamic social calendar, as well as a beautifully appointed club house offering fine and casual dining experiences.At the Moorings Yacht & Country Club in Vero Beach, Florida, whether you are a year-round or seasonal resident, just starting a family or enjoying retirement, our members quickly discover for themselves a rewarding atmosphere designed for play, relaxation, and renewal. We invite you to come and discover The Moorings Yacht & Country Club, where our staff is dedicated to delivering world class amenities and offering you an unsurpassed lifestyle!
